Package: salpa
Title: Satellite LiDAR Point Adjustment
Version: 0.0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Narumasa", "Tsutsumida", , "rsnaru.jp@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6333-0301"))
Description: A package for optimizing and adjusting satellite LiDAR point positions using genetic algorithms.
    The package provides tools for linear adjustment and location correction of spatial point data,
    particularly focused on satellite-based LiDAR observations.
